  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Goblintown: Really Hard Driving Game</strong> is a chaotic <strong>physics-based vehicular platformer</strong> where you race to make a delivery at the top of the most dangerous road in Goblintown. <strong>Scream into your microphone to slow down time</strong> and save yourself at the last second. Look for shortcuts to <strong>get the fastest time</strong>, and <strong>unlock new vehicles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/eb1ac43c2be60c454850bfb5d40180c4.poster.avif?t=1757692597\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/eb1ac43c2be60c454850bfb5d40180c4.webm?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/eb1ac43c2be60c454850bfb5d40180c4.mp4?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive your wobbly truck along a dangerous track filled with crazy jumps, explosives and obstacles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/044163700b6e0fd55c3e21be3095d0de.poster.avif?t=1757692597\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/044163700b6e0fd55c3e21be3095d0de.webm?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/044163700b6e0fd55c3e21be3095d0de.mp4?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your microphone to slow down time to save yourself at the last second.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/7c0de3467b77f7a7e6eb9a927cca6d6f.poster.avif?t=1757692597\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/7c0de3467b77f7a7e6eb9a927cca6d6f.webm?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/7c0de3467b77f7a7e6eb9a927cca6d6f.mp4?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges to unlock wacky new vehicles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/148098deb3215c747ed121791741505f.poster.avif?t=1757692597\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/148098deb3215c747ed121791741505f.webm?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417510/extras/148098deb3215c747ed121791741505f.mp4?t=1757692597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove your skills with global leaderboards for best times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
